UML:Comment.name: When HO creates one new item, he needs to input field in itembasic and also the fields in items, the StoreNo will be 0. Right after saving, he will be promped to input the information in ItemsAssort to detemin which stores these items will be copied to that is which stores will be able to see the items. Then system need to copy items to the stores specified here.
This entity specify the relationship between the composed item/Big Packing item and the child item.
One Item can have multiple Barcodes, but one Barcode only serves one item

Creating a new item include creating a new record in item_basic, creating a new record in items with store_no = 0, creating a new record in items_spec, creating a new record in items_price with store_no = 0. Right after saving, prompting user to set up the items_assort, that is to set up which regions/provinces/cities to download this item to.

When a new items is been created. After user has set up the itemsAssort(Regions/Provinces/Cities to be downloaded to), System need to automatically copy the new item to other stores. Tables need to be copied include: Items, Items_Price. Record in these two tables user created by default is 0 for the field of store_no. System need to copy records for all the real stores under the Region/Province/Cities defined in the itemsAssort.
